{"word":"σκιρτάω","slug":"σκιρτάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σκιρτάω</b></el> <el>(σκιρτάω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σκαίρω'><el>σκαίρω</el></a>\n<p/><i>to spring, leap, bound</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> of gusts of wind, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/>"}]}